&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of five years of experience as anesthesiologist, required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at epidurals, spinals and ultrasound-guided regional anesthesia, required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stand for long periods of time, required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in supervisory position, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team player, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certification(s):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Board certified in anesthesiology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doctor of Medicine degree with anesthesiology residency, required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
